":"","context":"In &quot;Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Sin \u0627\u0644\u0625\u062b\u0645","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/sin-al-ithm\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":40072,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2023\/05\/13\/jannah-blindness\/","url_meta":{"origin":36376,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Blindness: Paradise for patience with losing eyesight","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"May 13, 2023","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cAllah says: If I take the two noble eyes of My servant in this world, there is no reward for him with Me but Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 2400 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":18521,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2014\/03\/14\/best-kuhl-antimony\/","url_meta":{"origin":36376,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Kuhl: Best kind of kohl to use is antimony","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"March 14, 2014","format":false,"excerpt":"Ibn Abbas reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cVerily, the best of the kohl that you use is antimony, for it brightens the eyes and grows the hair.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Nasa\u0304'i\u0304 5113 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0628\u0652\u0646\u0650 \u0639\u064e\u0628\u0651\u064e\u0627\u0633\u064d \u0623\u064e\u0646\u0651\u064e \u0631\u064e\u0633\u064f\u0648\u0644\u064e \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u0650\u2026","rel":"","